snippet.textDisplay: Maybe Barb shouldn't have been as blunt as she was, although I think she felt like she had to defend herself as a result of backlash and ridicule she was getting on social media. I do agree with Chris that criticizing her son(no matter how much of it was warranted) on television was uncalled for. I do have to say though, that I thought Madison was very  disrespectful to Barb.
